Ly6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b2c14fdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170219%2F19933232&h=f0d4721c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170219/19933232</a><br />\n<br />\n人一死, 就無學術討論空間去探討起死回生之術. 所以自殺方法, 亦無學術討論空間可言."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"唔同意最後一段<br />\n「人一死就冇討論空間」<br />\n咁樣諗嘅話係咪唔洗諗點醫絕症？"}]}